data.description: Stunning all brick home on a cul de sac in the coveted Bluff at Bradbury location. Just minutes from exit 11, outside of city limits (county taxes only), and *no HOA*. The 18x36 inground saltwater pool w/ fountains, fenced yard, and 3 car garage are just a few of the many features you’ll love about this home! Inside you will find 4 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms, a bonus room which could be used as a 5th bedroom, formal dining area, spacious eat in kitchen with walk in pantry, island, beautiful *double sided* stone fireplace looking into great room, and catwalk above. Owner's suite is on the main level. Upstairs you have 3 additional bedrooms, one with an en suite full bath which could be used as a 2nd primary bedroom or guest suite along w/ another full bathroom and huge bonus room. Custom plantation shutters throughout and shed in back yard convey. Single garage depth was extended to accommodate a boat. You don’t find a home like this often so call and schedule your personal tour today!
